						               													<description>If the terms &amp;ldquo;Theater Sports&amp;rdquo; or &amp;ldquo;Whose Line Is It Anyway?&amp;rdquo; mean anything to you, you&amp;rsquo;ll recognize the spirit behind this Theatrical Styled party game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Impersonations, Charades, Jokes, Songs, Improvisation and more.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;From the early years of Decipher, Inc, Auditions at times resembles an elaborate version of Cranium, while at other times it seems like a party-event-in-a-box, reminiscent of a Murder Mystery Dinner Party, with Wayne Brady standing in for Sherlock Holmes.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;From the box:&amp;#10;AUDITIONS, the game&amp;#10;&amp;quot;everybody wants to get into the act&amp;quot; tm&amp;#10;Now you can too.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;See your friends in a whole new light - the spotlight - as Auditions turns your living room into center stage for the evening!&amp;#10;- See your button-down brother-in-law become the world's fattest ballerina!&amp;#10;- Hear your best friend as a TV evangelist begging for bucks!  Hallelujah!&amp;#10;- Experience your next door neighbors playing the hapless victims of the &amp;quot;Mattress Tag Police&amp;quot;&amp;#10;- You had no idea your mom knew THAT joke, or that ELVIS LIVES... in your great aunt Bertha!&amp;#10;- Witness your boss become... almost lifelike!  You'll laugh!  You'll cry!  You'll laugh 'til you cry!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;If you get a charge out of a great impersonation, appreciate a good joke or a clever charade, you'll love Auditions! Off-the-wall scripts, goofy songs and more, combine for an evening you'll never forget!  Play Auditions to get rave reviews!  Your family and friends will be begging for an encore!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
